# =============================================
# FORENSIC ANALYSIS INITIATION - R. v. LONGO
# =============================================

Write-Host "INITIATING COMPREHENSIVE FORENSIC ANALYSIS" -ForegroundColor Red
Write-Host "TIMESTAMP: $(Get-Date)" -ForegroundColor Yellow
Write-Host "CASE: R. v. Longo Constitutional Challenge" -ForegroundColor Yellow

# Create Forensic Workspace
$ForensicPath = "C:\Forensic_Analysis_$(Get-Date -Format 'yyyyMMdd_HHmmss')"
New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $ForensicPath -Force
Write-Host "Forensic Workspace Created: $ForensicPath" -ForegroundColor Green

# =============================================
# PHASE 1: SYSTEM INVENTORY & HASH VERIFICATION
# =============================================

Write-Host "`nPHASE 1: SYSTEM INVENTORY & HASH VERIFICATION" -ForegroundColor Cyan

# Search for Francesco Longo related files across all drives
$SearchTerms = @("Longo", "Francesco", "R_v_Longo", "Windsor", "Crown", "LAO", "HRTO", "Ombudsman")
$Drives = Get-PSDrive -PSProvider FileSystem | Where-Object {$_.Root -ne 'C:\' -and $_.Root -ne 'A:\'}

$AllEvidenceFiles = @()
foreach ($Drive in $Drives) {
    Write-Host "Scanning Drive: $($Drive.Root)" -ForegroundColor Yellow
    foreach ($Term in $SearchTerms) {
        $Files = Get-ChildItem -Path $Drive.Root -Recurse -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | 
                Where-Object {$_.Name -like "*$Term*" -or $_.Extension -match '\.(pdf|doc|xls|mp3|m4a|wav|msg|eml)$'}
        $AllEvidenceFiles += $Files
    }
}

# Generate Comprehensive Inventory with Hashes
$EvidenceInventory = $AllEvidenceFiles | Select-Object @(
    @{Name="FullName"; Expression={$_.FullName}},
    @{Name="Name"; Expression={$_.Name}},
    @{Name="Directory"; Expression={$_.DirectoryName}},
    @{Name="Size_KB"; Expression={[math]::Round($_.Length/1KB, 2)}},
    @{Name="Created"; Expression={$_.CreationTime}},
    @{Name="Modified"; Expression={$_.LastWriteTime}},
    @{Name="Extension"; Expression={$_.Extension}},
    @{Name="SHA256"; Expression={(Get-FileHash $_.FullName -Algorithm SHA256 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue).Hash}}
)

$EvidenceInventory | Export-Csv "$ForensicPath\Evidence_Inventory.csv" -NoTypeInformation
Write-Host "Evidence Inventory Complete: $($EvidenceInventory.Count) files catalogued" -ForegroundColor Green

# =============================================
# PHASE 2: JULY 4TH TRAP ANALYSIS
# =============================================

Write-Host "`nPHASE 2: JULY 4TH TRAP ANALYSIS" -ForegroundColor Cyan

# Analyze files around July 4th timeline
$July4Files = $EvidenceInventory | Where-Object {
    $_.Created -like "*2024-07-04*" -or 
    $_.Modified -like "*2024-07-04*" -or
    $_.Name -like "*July4*" -or 
    $_.Name -like "*0704*"
}

$July4Files | Export-Csv "$ForensicPath\July4_Trap_Files.csv" -NoTypeInformation
Write-Host "July 4th Trap Analysis: $($July4Files.Count) files identified" -ForegroundColor Green

# =============================================
# PHASE 3: AUDIO EVIDENCE PROCESSING
# =============================================

Write-Host "`nPHASE 3: AUDIO EVIDENCE PROCESSING" -ForegroundColor Cyan

$AudioFiles = $EvidenceInventory | Where-Object {$_.Extension -match '\.(mp3|m4a|wav)$'}
$AudioAnalysis = $AudioFiles | ForEach-Object {
    [PSCustomObject]@{
        FileName = $_.Name
        FilePath = $_.FullName
        Size_MB = [math]::Round($_.Size_KB/1024, 2)
        Created = $_.Created
        Modified = $_.Modified
        SHA256 = $_.SHA256
        Priority = if($_.Name -match "LAO|Crown|Judge|Ashley|Batiston|Joy") {"HIGH"} else {"MEDIUM"}
        Status = "NEEDS_TRANSCRIPTION"
    }
}

$AudioAnalysis | Export-Csv "$ForensicPath\Audio_Evidence_Analysis.csv" -NoTypeInformation
Write-Host "Audio Evidence Catalogued: $($AudioFiles.Count) files" -ForegroundColor Green

# =============================================
# PHASE 4: EMAIL & DOCUMENT ANALYSIS
# =============================================

Write-Host "`nPHASE 4: EMAIL & DOCUMENT ANALYSIS" -ForegroundColor Cyan

$EmailFiles = $EvidenceInventory | Where-Object {$_.Extension -match '\.(msg|eml)$'}
$DocumentFiles = $EvidenceInventory | Where-Object {$_.Extension -match '\.(pdf|doc|docx)$'}

$EmailAnalysis = $EmailFiles | ForEach-Object {
    [PSCustomObject]@{
        FileName = $_.Name
        FilePath = $_.FullName
        Type = "EMAIL"
        Created = $_.Created
        Modified = $_.Modified
        SHA256 = $_.SHA256
        Agency = if($_.Name -match "LAO"){"Legal Aid"}elseif($_.Name -match "Crown|Batiston|Joy"){"Crown Office"}elseif($_.Name -match "WPS|Police"){"Police"}else{"Unknown"}
    }
}

$DocumentAnalysis = $DocumentFiles | ForEach-Object {
    [PSCustomObject]@{
        FileName = $_.Name
        FilePath = $_.FullName
        Type = "DOCUMENT"
        Created = $_.Created
        Modified = $_.Modified
        SHA256 = $_.SHA256
        Category = if($_.Name -match "Motion|Filing"){"Court Filing"}elseif($_.Name -match "Disclosure"){"Disclosure"}elseif($_.Name -match "Complaint"){"Complaint"}else{"Legal Document"}
    }
}

$EmailAnalysis | Export-Csv "$ForensicPath\Email_Analysis.csv" -NoTypeInformation
$DocumentAnalysis | Export-Csv "$ForensicPath\Document_Analysis.csv" -NoTypeInformation
Write-Host "Email Analysis: $($EmailFiles.Count) files" -ForegroundColor Green
Write-Host "Document Analysis: $($DocumentFiles.Count) files" -ForegroundColor Green

# =============================================
# PHASE 5: SYSTEMIC CORRUPTION PATTERN ANALYSIS
# =============================================

Write-Host "`nPHASE 5: SYSTEMIC CORRUPTION PATTERN ANALYSIS" -ForegroundColor Cyan

# Create Agency Coordination Matrix
$Agencies = @(
    "Windsor Police Service",
    "Crown Attorney Office", 
    "Legal Aid Ontario",
    "Ontario Court of Justice",
    "Law Society of Ontario",
    "HRTO",
    "Ontario Ombudsman",
    "RCMP/OPP"
)

$CoordinationMatrix = @()
foreach ($SourceAgency in $Agencies) {
    foreach ($TargetAgency in $Agencies) {
        if ($SourceAgency -ne $TargetAgency) {
            $EvidenceCount = ($EvidenceInventory | Where-Object {
                $_.Name -match $SourceAgency -and $_.Name -match $TargetAgency
            }).Count
            
            $CoordinationMatrix += [PSCustomObject]@{
                Source_Agency = $SourceAgency
                Target_Agency = $TargetAgency  
                Evidence_Files_Count = $EvidenceCount
                Coordination_Level = if($EvidenceCount -gt 0){"CONFIRMED"}else{"POTENTIAL"}
                Pattern_Type = "INTER-AGENCY_COORDINATION"
            }
        }
    }
}

$CoordinationMatrix | Export-Csv "$ForensicPath\Agency_Coordination_Matrix.csv" -NoTypeInformation

# =============================================
# PHASE 6: TIMELINE RECONSTRUCTION
# =============================================

Write-Host "`nPHASE 6: TIMELINE RECONSTRUCTION" -ForegroundColor Cyan

$TimelineEvents = $EvidenceInventory | ForEach-Object {
    [PSCustomObject]@{
        Event_Date = $_.Created
        File_Name = $_.Name
        File_Type = $_.Extension
        Event_Type = if($_.Name -match "Motion"){"Court Filing"}elseif($_.Name -match "Email"){"Communication"}elseif($_.Name -match "Audio"){"Recording"}else{"Document"}
        Agency_Involved = if($_.Name -match "LAO"){"Legal Aid"}elseif($_.Name -match "Crown"){"Crown Office"}elseif($_.Name -match "WPS"){"Police"}elseif($_.Name -match "Court|Judge"){"Judiciary"}else{"Multiple"}
        Legal_Significance = if($_.Created -like "*2024-07-04*"){"JULY4_TRAP"}else{"EVIDENCE"}
    }
} | Sort-Object Event_Date

$TimelineEvents | Export-Csv "$ForensicPath\Timeline_Reconstruction.csv" -NoTypeInformation
